description.en:
What is the project about?
WE ARE GANGS RABBIT!! Gangster Rabbit: Evolution is a collection of 7777 Gangs — unique avatars hosted on the Ethereum blockchain.Your Gangster grants you access to a community comprised of 50 gangs, each one representing distinct characteristics.
In the fight for supremacy, hierarchy is vital. GAS: Evolution employs a dual-rarity system. The first rarity layer is determined by the gang your Gangster belongs to. The second layer is a factor of your Gangster’s traits.The GangsRabbit army has been deployed with advanced equipment Jetpack - Airplane - Car to be able to conduct monster killing campaigns & collect $RABBIT for stockpile. Journey to kill enemies and run endlessly Like Endless GangsRabbit 

What makes your project unique?
Supported by social media influencers & 600++ KOLS, No Token & No Unlock Development Team, Big Marketing Wallet, Renounced ownership, DIDBTOK, AMABinance, Super Burn token, Marketing MiniDoge x200 in the past, KYC-AUDIT - BASED - TAX REDUCTION , CEX PRE-LIST on VINDAX, 3% tax reward holder ,  Binance Live - Binance Post, CG , CMC , CG China, CMC China 12-48hrs, Mint 777 GangsNfts at launch, Game Run & Shoot , 600++ Kols & Twitter influencers

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
Used $35000 for BINANCE , Huobi , BTOK , Marketing....Before launch.
